{"data":[{"id":560953430,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"95a8c5070afe88370ee075523ba5b05c","url_token":"sfireworks","name":"fireworks","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c975b3ae251743ca1949618e857ad2fd_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c975b3ae251743ca1949618e857ad2fd_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/95a8c5070afe88370ee075523ba5b05c","user_type":"people","headline":"数声风笛离亭晚，君向潇湘我向秦。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560953430","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545901762,"updated_time":1545901762,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e让我想起了我高中时隔壁班一位号称推翻相对论的同学，觉得自己不用参加高考了，结果当然是无稽之谈，就是学习压力太大想逃避而已。而且那位同学最后还是因为精神压力过大回家调整了好久才回到学校。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果一个人能够证明哥德巴赫猜想，那么他肯定是热爱数学，是一个有一定科学研究素养的人。这样的人如果对这种重磅问题有了头绪肯定不是藏着掖着，会第一时间与别人分享自己的方法和思路。科学的进步就是不断质疑的过程，经得住质疑的就是对的，经不住的就是错的，但是无论是对是错，与别人讨论和分析的过程一定会让自己有收获。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以就从这个“1月1号在知乎发表证明”这种卖关子的行为，我觉得这实在不是一个解决了重大科学问题的人所做的，应该就是个炒作吧\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560006326,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"84c05ad37ba0eeabd6ba4b2d5a571932","url_token":"wei-wu-xian-62-26","name":"魏无羡","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/84c05ad37ba0eeabd6ba4b2d5a571932","user_type":"people","headline":"微博20粉丝红人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560006326","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545801100,"updated_time":1545801100,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":49,"content":"\u003cp\u003e民科预定，戏说不是胡说，哥猜不是乱猜。说到民科，我就想起哥德巴赫的猜想。明年原旦，由我解开的哥猜论文即将发布。我将继承数学家哥德巴赫，我会用全新的哥德巴赫形象努力创造一个让大家都满意的数学鬼才。文体两爆炸，弘扬数学文化。请大家多多支持。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560905731,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1d93105a04313344c89c9449444b0e8b","url_token":"starry-child","name":"Unstarry","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-513bdcfa43610e8a5ca81dc0b5fc8132_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-513bdcfa43610e8a5ca81dc0b5fc8132_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1d93105a04313344c89c9449444b0e8b","user_type":"people","headline":"成长中……","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560905731","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545897950,"updated_time":1546273480,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":36,"content":"\u003cp\u003e最后一更，看了一下这大哥的证明，过于沙雕，新年快乐源泉……再说一遍，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记得取关，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记得取关，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e记得取关!\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e开始辣!新的一年从看哥德巴赫猜想开始!各位2019快乐\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e球球你们取关了，35k的关注看的我心痛\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e短短一天的造势，提问者就收获快千条回答和12k的关注，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e混这么久知乎\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e心态崩了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生，哥德巴赫猜想，清华北大，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e提问的方式太抓痛点了，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e多少人也幻想过自己独立解决千古难题，功成名就，一步登天，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我写下第一个知乎回答还老想着能收获很多赞，一跃成为大v，走向人生巅峰。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后回想起自己灰尘满布的现实，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e梦想甩开能力太远，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e无力，痛哭，呐喊，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之后我们成长，选择，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有人依然难以服输，也有人拥抱无奈，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也有人正在经历这个过程，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以能看到有不断的鼓励，也有严厉的警告和批评。和提问者年龄相差不大的少年们肯定大多还是相信梦想的光辉，也愿意更多的宽容，因为这也是对自己的一种宽容。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e历经现实的各位深知现实的尖锐，所以话语可能也会咄咄逼人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e虽然我们想多一些宽容，但是很可惜，哥德巴赫猜想不会因为你是高中生变得宽容，这块铁壁上镌刻了多少人的岁月。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e是，每个人都值得宽容\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么不对那些人多一些宽容，多一些尊重。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e牺牲自己毕生去研究，深埋历史的尘土，化作养料，等待一个集大成者去摘取果实。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这就是很多无名的科学研究者。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没有化作养料的觉悟，一心想着摘取果实，对这种想法还施以无限的宽容，对这些奉献者们是不是太过残酷？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想传承科学的火焰，请记住你不是手持火把，你也是柴薪。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于一个人，一个高中生，给予宽容，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e让他继续保持对数学的热情，去认识研究的正确的方式方法。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但对于他的行为，错的就是要批评，不切实际的幻想要打碎。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不要站在已经点燃的篝火旁边玩弄火焰还对不断向前的探索者诘问。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，现在说的有点绝对，等元旦见分晓。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但还是持悲观态度。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，我还是想成为大v( ᵒ̴̶̷̥́ωᵒ̴̶̷̣̥̀ )\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了知乎2018年度总结，自己的回答被浏览了上万次，虽然收获的赞/浏览数过于悲伤，但我也深知自己的回答并不是多么优秀，不过我还是衷心希望自己的回答能有所帮助，如果你喜欢，请给个赞吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559588038,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"42f40cdf735f03cd9fc7fb919dabb48f","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559588038","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545741720,"updated_time":1545741720,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":39,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主加油！我也是在高中时期就发明了永动机，最后保送到名校的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真的不是很懂为什么这么多人都对题主冷嘲热讽，不说了，期待题主的论文，如果真的证明了，我一定帮你预订床位！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563104367,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cd1372650d71e6ccbed79063dceef58b","url_token":"wu-yao-wang-zhi-lei","name":"巫妖王之泪","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2c59ec55f500b8c3c560ba2ca124bc57_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2c59ec55f500b8c3c560ba2ca124bc57_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/cd1372650d71e6ccbed79063dceef58b","user_type":"people","headline":"真理追求者，世界创造者，幻想者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563104367","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546181844,"updated_time":1546317766,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":33,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2019年一月一日修改，看到负质数就不想看了，借用我上交同学的评价——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003enot even wrong。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e补充一点：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这次居然还真的有人认为他能证明出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使是证明失败以后居然还真的有人还在假设万一他证明出来了你们是不是怎么怎么......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是我这两天对知乎最失望的地方。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下原文：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e肯定是失败，不存在成功的可能性，最微小的可能性都没有，就是零。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这没什么好说的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想说的是，那些在评论区对他进行鼓励的人，那些对这个孩子吹鼓所谓的“梦想”的人，那些对这个孩子说什么相信自己，“他只是个孩子要鼓励”的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e非蠢既坏!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，大多数只是蠢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e几万人的冷嘲热讽才是正常的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这总比鼓励他，吹鼓所谓的梦想好。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这孩子最后要是成为一个民科，或者在你们所谓的鼓励之下专注哥猜忽视高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们很可能就把这个孩子毁了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们根本不知道证明哥猜的难度，没有对这种困扰人类智力最顶尖那群人几百年的难题有着最基本的敬畏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中生宣称用基本数学证明哥猜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这根本就是一种侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e侮辱1742年至今为止的数学界，侮辱欧拉高数希尔伯特等等这些人类古往今来的智力最高峰。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们这种鼓励相当于对一个跑万米马拉松的新生儿喊加油。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们是在害了他。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563779589,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7332f492dc2db7f8f9fc3400572b63b2","url_token":"evil-wu-xin","name":"evil无心","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/38fc418d359b82f191f61bea44619edb_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/38fc418d359b82f191f61bea44619edb_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7332f492dc2db7f8f9fc3400572b63b2","user_type":"people","headline":"保san值需远离：他她祂牠","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563779589","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275978,"updated_time":1546275978,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e没有半点干货，只卖人设，一个周涨近三万五千粉丝，可以称得上是营销界的翘楚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e包装一下留下过程证据，用这个证明自己在营销方面的才能，过几个211 985学校的新闻学传播学初审还是有机会的。（有些学校比较重视过程性评价，说不定会破格让你过，这也是未来自招趋势。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e祝文体 正负两开花 \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563804523,"type":"answer","an