zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95b91caf5b82c96c5f79233d7c15620b_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95b91caf5b82c96c5f79233d7c15620b_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7f092effaf9969aaac10fadf09dbdcf8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f5eee6ea7eb5bea35134a847b0414d24_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7f092effaf9969aaac10fadf09dbdcf8_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f5eee6ea7eb5bea35134a847b0414d24_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7f092effaf9969aaac10fadf09dbdcf8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7f092effaf9969aaac10fadf09dbdcf8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560463646,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560463646","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839753,"updated_time":1545839753,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":389,"content":"\u003cp\u003e哥们，这么和你说说吧。你的证明基本上不用看肯定是错的。但是我还是期待能看到你的论文，因为通过论文大概能看出来你是随便写着玩的还是真的认真自学了大学数学开始思考这个问题的。如果是后者的话你的求知欲和学习能力都是非常难能可贵的，我建议你暂时忘了猜想认认真真复习高考的科目，考一个好一些的大学的数学系，把对数学的热情持续下去，做研究、读博。也许有一天会在某个问题上有自己的独特见解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望你不要变得像某些知乎er一样，生活中蝇营狗苟，在网上通过嘲讽别人为乐。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保持这股热情，去冲刺数学的高峰吧！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561952097,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561952097","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c5f5d51b2acf86809734c87c3df6edd6_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546020616,"updated_time":1546276161,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":126,"content":"\u003cp\u003e大部分声称能证明哥德巴赫猜想的人都不会做下面三个题目（相当多的一部分会死在前面两题）： \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（1）给定任意一个大于4的偶数，存在两个素数，它们的和大于这个给定的偶数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（2）给定任意一个大于4的偶数，存在两个素数，它们的和小于或等于这个给定的偶数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（3）叙述并证明「素数定理」。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是个屡试不爽的照妖镜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c8c21e64bace6c4d9fcea663bdc6b28_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"703\" data-rawheight=\"241\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c8c21e64bace6c4d9fcea663bdc6b28_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"703\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c8c21e64bace6c4d9fcea663bdc6b28_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='703'%20height='241'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"703\" data-rawheight=\"241\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c8c21e64bace6c4d9fcea663bdc6b28_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"703\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c8c21e64bace6c4d9fcea663bdc6b28_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c8c21e64bace6c4d9fcea663bdc6b28_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e ：如果你能用准确无误的数学语言给出这三个问题的证明，并且在\u003cb\u003e2018年12月30日\u003c/b\u003e之前在知乎发布，我就把我的advisor的联系方式告诉你。他是美国的数论专家，这个学期正好在sabbatical，可以破例审查你的哥德巴赫猜想「证明」。\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e如果你不能在\u003cb\u003e2018年12月30日\u003c/b\u003e前给出答案，可以肯定你是个愚弄广大群众的网络骗子。请你在\u003cb\u003e2018年12月31日\u003c/b\u003e前将你的钓鱼问题删除，让大家迎来一个健康，愉快的新年。\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e「我叫你一声，你敢答应吗？」\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下面是本回答的链接：\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307030887/answer/561951161\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如何看待高中生声称证明哥德巴赫猜想？\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e祝你平安。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e更新：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e拜读了你发布的所谓「\u003ca href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53643064\" class=\"internal\"\u003e证明\u003c/a\u003e」。忍不住要称赞一句：字写的挺工整的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你基本证明了三句不需要任何证明的废话：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥德巴赫猜想成立\u003cb\u003e或者\u003c/b\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29\" alt=\"2n=(-1)+(2n+1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥德巴赫猜想成立\u003cb\u003e或者\u003c/b\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-3%29%2B%282n%2B3%29\" alt=\"2n=(-3)+(2n+3)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥德巴赫猜想成立\u003cb\u003e或者\u003c/b\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-5%29%2B%282n%2B5%29\" alt=\"2n=(-5)+(2n+5)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后，你用极其混乱的逻辑，\u003cb\u003e否定\u003c/b\u003e了下面三条\u003cb\u003e真命题\u003c/b\u003e：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-1%29%2B%282n%2B1%29\" alt=\"2n=(-1)+(2n+1)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-3%29%2B%282n%2B3%29\" alt=\"2n=(-3)+(2n+3)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e对于任意正整数 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n\" alt=\"n\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ， \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n%3D%28-5%29%2B%282n%2B5%29\" alt=\"2n=(-5)+(2n+5)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ；\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后你宣布：哥德巴赫猜想成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e回头是岸吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e新年快乐。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561086729,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c32ad3f421f57eaa80782e51ec6a5bde","url_token":"liaoxuefeng","name":"廖雪峰","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/17237388534b0df48ec200192bb45cc4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/17237388534b0df48ec200192bb45cc4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c32ad3f421f57eaa80782e51ec6a5bde","user_type":"people","headline":"业余马拉松选手 \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.liaoxuefeng.com\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttp://www.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003eliaoxuefeng.com\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561086729","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545915097,"updated_time":1545959750,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":38,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可以考虑《私人订制》\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问：我证明了哥德巴赫猜想，能保送进清华吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e葛优：那哪行啊，不是说您不行，是清华这座小庙，怎么容得下您这尊大神！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问：那我能去哪儿？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e葛优：巧了！昨中国科学院数学研究院院长还问我来着，下个月他就退休了，可惜了现在还没找好接班人，让我给他推荐一个，我这两天正琢磨着，嘿，碰上您了！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（自行脑补……）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563850317,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","questi