5db_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/4b9006e87ca5787038f994d7978275db_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8863e75ee6e1c509f0e348efaddc575a","user_type":"people","headline":"客栈老板/网文作家/绳艺爱好者","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562550457","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9903c4f0a7943afac242fea147b5a72a_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546099394,"updated_time":1546099394,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":23,"content":"\u003cp\u003e铁定能！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过题主你得跑快点，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e中科院数学所、北大清华外面宣称自己证明了哥德巴赫猜想的人一堆一堆的，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你可别被他们抢先了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-92e2186902add8df7ecd970c70815b3d_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"376\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b133faecb63439ab4f7425a42b0c0bd5_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-92e2186902add8df7ecd970c70815b3d_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='376'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"376\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b133faecb63439ab4f7425a42b0c0bd5_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-92e2186902add8df7ecd970c70815b3d_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-92e2186902add8df7ecd970c70815b3d_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后提醒下，据说想进数学所必须先在门卫那儿答对五道题，可别进不去啊。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561442293,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fa44a989f73510f2663f98e515997faf","url_token":"starcraft-65-23","name":"魅影永恒","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-482766926b278db6c2bd82007c08f184_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-482766926b278db6c2bd82007c08f184_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fa44a989f73510f2663f98e515997faf","user_type":"people","headline":"在校大学生 一个文艺的数学系渣渣","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561442293","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-069b4f26422728360ccbc68a09ea07f0_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545967887,"updated_time":1546274808,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":26,"content":"\u003cp\u003e荒谬绝伦。。。这好像真的不是炒作，这就是不好好学习，还做梦。浪费我拉屎时间。。。我真的觉得看了负质数三个字之后还打起精神认真研究的我好蠢。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e既然已经最坏的恶意了，那我再深一点，看看这个头像，嘲笑与戏谑写满了丑陋的脸，这提问者是想证明一个新注册的号就可以用几千字的东西搅动知乎?证明这个自称理性的社区其实与他们轻视的别无二致?证明所谓的破万关注并非需要多少努力?如果真是这样的话，知乎怕是要从此衰落，再也没有认真答题的人了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4d7a59d9a52e7e27848e71d6db6554d4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4d7a59d9a52e7e27848e71d6db6554d4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到大家这么踊跃的回答，大多数都抱有善意，即使是泼冷水也很有理有据的希望拯救一个迷途的孩子，在这里我就做一次恶人吧……“我向来是不惮以最坏的恶意揣测中国人的”，当我好奇点进题主的主页之后，发现他已经拿到了17k的关注……我斗胆用“最坏的恶意”揣测一下，莫不是想借着这个事情，博流量和关注的吧?2019年元旦证明发表之后无论对错想必会再有一次关注的爆发，尘埃散尽之后，这次闹剧中积累的流量或许有变现的途径?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，如果你真的证明成功的话，那我愿意为你送上真挚的祝福\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557868356,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"32d4841a959e391de889f387b0572bad","url_token":"bu-meng-de-xiao-peng-you-37","name":"纯善的不良少年","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7651700edb8ae622d6e62f2368855fa4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7651700edb8ae622d6e62f2368855fa4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/32d4841a959e391de889f387b0572bad","user_type":"people","headline":"数学小萌新，潜水爱好者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557868356","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545538184,"updated_time":1545620756,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":38,"content":"\u003cp\u003e小朋友...你发文章啊\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你学过additive 和 multiplicative number theory吗？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561406516,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"37a738135f440f85fe581a0f8b2835b3","url_token":"chen-zhi-cheng-97-20","name":"Dominix","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab45b70dd3292794ad47e89d40394edc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ab45b70dd3292794ad47e89d40394edc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/37a738135f440f85fe581a0f8b2835b3","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561406516","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-256eced1603068ccd0bdb0801e9386ed_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545965331,"updated_time":1545965405,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":30,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真能证明得出，我就在本回答的评论中随机抽中一位关注我的知友，赠送Feather AS D2 不锈钢手动剃须刀一把，绝不食言。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f44aef4223773b8e1d742eb31c19607b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f44aef4223773b8e1d742eb31c19607b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563762242,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1d9db11f3d28722ffe58405edcaeae38","url_token":"wu-da-you-47-19","name":"井下","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c028cb0fd73d154e5d6e881cd69cccad_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c028cb0fd73d154e5d6e881cd69cccad_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1d9db11f3d28722ffe58405edcaeae38","user_type":"people","headline":"瞎想的人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563762242","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273897,"updated_time":1546277840,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":29,"content":"\u003cp\u003e特来编辑一下现有证明中的疑问，知识浅薄，将将疑问逐一列举， \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 请题主回答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e假定“-1”为且是唯一的负质数，为何对于任意正整数n, 2n属于集合A\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e2n属于B 和 2n=(-1)+(2n+1)的逻辑关联为何是或，而不是且，两者并不构成或的逻辑关系\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e实在看不下去了，洗洗睡吧\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e算了，我还是编辑下题主的论证逻辑吧：\u003c/li\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e存在负质数\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e集合B即为所有满足哥猜的偶数集\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e那么对于任意偶数2n, 2n属于集合A \u003cb\u003e\u003ci\u003e或 \u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e2n属于集合B（注意“或”)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e补充“变式一”，定义“-1”为负质数。因为6k+2此时不属于集合A，所以属于集合B\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e补充“变式二”，定义“-3”为负质数。因为6k此时不属于集合A，所以属于集合B\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e补充“变式三”，定义“-5”为负质数。因为6k-2此时不属于集合A，所以属于集合B\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e哥猜得证\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cli\u003e那么来看下答主究竟证明了什么：对于任意偶数，其加上一个\u003cb\u003e特定\u003c/b\u003e奇数后，一定是一个合数\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e妙极\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e再补充一下“变式一，二，三”的证明逻辑吧，\u003c/li\u003e\u003col\u003e\u003cli\u003e2n+1, 2n+3, 2n+5均为质数，（对于任意正整数n）\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e因为A是所有质数对（包括负质数）之和的集合，\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e又因为所有偶数2n都可以表达成\"-1\"+\"2n+1\",\"-3\"+\"2n+3\",\"-5\"+\"2n+5\"的格式\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e所以若存在偶数2n, 2n不属于集合A，则\"-1\",\"-3\",\"-5\"不是质数（逆否命题）\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e所以若2不属于A，则\"-1\",\"-3\",\"-5\"不是质数\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e（此步为答主揣测，已答主微薄的知识水平，不足以理解大佬的用意）：题主疑似默认2属于集合A。\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e因此\"-1\",\"-3\",\"-5\"均为负质数，（别唯一了，不然直接前后矛盾了）\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e又因为7.1，2n+1,2n+3,2n+5均为质数\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e所以2n如果不是正质数对的和（集合B），就一定是集合A中的元素。（别问为什么）\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e变式成立\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e妙极\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e分割线：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或许题主已经跨过抽象大关，所以答主这种还徘徊在逻辑关的人无法理解复杂的思维。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过也不用太过较真，敢于把自己的证明po在如此大的平台上的还是有十分大的勇气的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e此前答主私以为用图论的知识证明了平面上不能存在5个两两相邻的图形，就是证明了四色问题，还很是开心了一会儿，谁没年轻过呢\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至少证明大佬的这次回答很大程度上又激发起了年轻人研究哥猜的兴趣，抛砖引玉，说不定看到此条的你就证明出了哥猜呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（顺道设想一下如果大佬不卖关子的话，zhihu或成为最大的学术思想讨论平台也未可知呀）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559739517,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bfe7f9abcbc9202a2b8adda00f11019f","url_token":"chen-jing-76-80","name":"陈京","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/06e1e0820fc6e6e7cc23a61d1aeb512f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/06e1e0820fc6e6e7cc23a61d1aeb512f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bfe7f9abcbc9202a2b8adda00f11019f","user_type":"people","headline":"资深工程造价人员。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559739517","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545757415,"updated_time":1545758783,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":107,"content":"\u003cp\u003e大晚上的，我正在加班做商务标，实在是搞不下去了抽空看看知乎，怎么就看到这么搞笑的一道问题儿……容我先笑几分钟……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本人不才，数学方面最高荣誉是中学阶段的奥赛广东省二等奖，以及高考数学基本满分，所以我觉得我有资格回答此问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的回答是：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，则不需要保送。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e这个问题有点类似于：(在单注情况下)我兜里有3600万元，正好能把双色球所有的组合统统买下来，那么我是不是就能中500万呢……\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e答案是：肯定可以啦！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e不过你既然有3600万元，为啥要中这区区500万？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e你都能证明哥猜，你还会看得上区区清北？？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e所以，题主就是个数学基本没入门、不知天高地厚的生瓜蛋子一个……大家随便笑笑就散了吧……\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我继续做标书去了……哈哈哈哈……真搞笑这个问题。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e我知道我语气不甚友好，为免题主这种民科（很有可能是杠精）影响我的心情，所以关闭评论。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561690739,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d965a5be682e917ea1b4b55971487688","url_token":"san-shi-qiu-feng","name":"三世秋风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d965a5be682e917ea1b4b55971487688","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561690739","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545989647,"updated_time":1546265832,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":34,"content":"\u003cp\u003e       兄弟，我也是一名高中生，我曾经也很骄傲，但我有自知之明，我能独立推出一元三次方程通解，能独立得出严谨的极限定义，思考出微积分很浅显的基本思想，得到了数学老师的认可，我话放在这，你要是真能证明出来，我就这辈子都服气了，服服气气的，我连牛顿，爱因斯坦都不服气，想要比一比，作为目标。你要是证出来，我将来再也不碰数学，放弃数学，你就是个天才，天才中的天才。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       正经说一下，我曾经也是一个很骄傲的人，总想做些什么，之前我得出ε-δ极限定义与微积分的基本思想后，也曾经想自己发展出整个微积分的领域，但是，我后来明白，这只是我不自量力而已，在老师推荐下，我看了高等数学的书，我才明白我的微积分思想和真正的微积分差距有多大，现代数学的发展是无数人积累的成果，我们应该有敬畏之心，我后来发誓，在不学完数学知识，就再也不碰这些玄学命题，因为这只是徒劳无功而已，我必须学习前人的智慧，戒骄戒躁，踏踏实实的去学，去思考，才是正途，想要忽视差距对我们一般人来说是不可能的，那无疑是天才中的天才，人类之子，希望能与君共勉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        更新\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        这几天总感觉不对劲，我突然发现，他不是认为自己比得上那些数学家，也不是没意识到问题的难度，他只是在拼，拼运气，拼那无比渺小的几率，拼他正好发现了证明方法，就好比高尔夫选手进洞拼技术，他就像一个普通人，他也去参加高尔夫国际比赛，但他拼运气，拼他能百分百进洞，球球进洞\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        更新12月31日10点12分\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         还有14小时我们就要见证历史了，特地留念，话说原来知乎的赞真的这么难拿，才16个赞，各位路过的没事点个赞吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         更新12月31日20点33分\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         好鸡冻啊，忍不住又来发点东西，明天还有课，今晚就不等 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 了，明天看，各位如果有呆到零点的记得把感想评论一下哈，明天我来上手第一手资料，请尽情发挥自己的文采\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         最后，如果明天你没证出来，那你就在此地等候，我去买两个橘子，祝大家文体...  ...     ......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       更新\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       感觉我尾巴又要翘起来了，反省一下，我能做出那些其实是因为我们高中很多题目的解法都有一些先进的思想包含在内，就是说我无形之中借助了很多信息，和那些从无到有独立发现出来的数学家还是有很大差距的，我认为我还是不行的啊，从学成绩来看，也不怕你们笑话，我一直都是垫底的，高一还好点，后面都垫底了，无力学习\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563761534,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6d40f3e42e9c6434029593031e345b3","url_token":"hjihao","name":"豪豪","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f3d81cdef413892dc90b806c17a34c0d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f3d81cdef413892dc90b806c17a34c0d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6d40f3e42e9c6434029593031e345b3","user_type":"people","headline":"陌上花开 馥蕊柏然","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563761534","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8b8780ec8561af3e6d790e7df11cbd33_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273803,"updated_time":1546277366,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":30,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我看懂了他的逻辑。大框架没有错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只是他的工作是，解释了: 任意大于2的偶数总能写成两个奇数之和。(即哥德巴赫猜想的逆命题。下图是刚刚看见的，完美解释了思路)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d5e5b1fbb8080c255cd9fc302a034398_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1531\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-229e813837f2401161b32daeab057b2c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d5e5b1fbb8080c255cd9fc302a034398_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1531'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1531\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-229e813837f2401161b32daeab057b2c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d5e5b1fbb8080c255cd9fc302a034398_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d5e5b1fbb8080c255cd9fc302a034398_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e—— ——————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说一下\"证明过程\"大家为什么会看得云里雾里，以第一变式为例: \u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6b515ef7d75da6923ea9f012669489_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2769\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f839558e40cc1235ab2dbef60620e332_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2769\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6b515ef7d75da6923ea9f012669489_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='2769'%20height='1280'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"2769\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f839558e40cc1235ab2dbef60620e332_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2769\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6b515ef7d75da6923ea9f012669489_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7b6b515ef7d75da6923ea9f012669489_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e属于\"偷换概念\"。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有我觉得大家不要抠着那个-1不是质数。我想证明者本意是构造出一个新的集合，姑且称为\"六集\"，里面囊括了满足哥猜的所有偶数和它塞入的负数，然后\"鬼斧神工\"(注: 这个词属误用，只能用来形容大自然——高考语文了解一下，敲黑板划重点) 般证明出这个集合实际上筛去那个负数就剩全体大于2的偶数，那么这个逻辑是没有问题的。 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e是中间的证明走江湖了。祝愿他在新的一年能有所改变，脚踏实地，仰望星空。PS: 有些人揪着那个-1瞎凑热闹，是要向全国人民谢罪的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=120\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=80\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
